JOIN patient_mortality pm ON le.HADM_ID = pm.HADM_ID
GROUP BY pm.mortality_status

rules.fixed_sql:
WITH sepsis_patients AS ( 
    SELECT DISTINCT icu.HADM_ID 
    FROM ICUSTAYS icu 
    JOIN PROCEDURES_ICD proc ON icu.HADM_ID = proc.HADM_ID 
    JOIN DIAGNOSES_ICD diag ON icu.HADM_ID = diag.HADM_ID 
    JOIN D_ICD_DIAGNOSES dict ON diag.ICD_CODE = dict.ICD_CODE AND diag.ICD_VERSION = dict.ICD_VERSION 
    WHERE proc.ICD_CODE = '3895' AND proc.ICD_VERSION = 9 
    AND ((diag.ICD_VERSION = 10 AND diag.ICD_CODE LIKE 'A40%') 
         OR (diag.ICD_VERSION = 10 AND diag.ICD_CODE LIKE 'A41%') 
         OR (diag.ICD_VERSION = 10 AND diag.ICD_CODE LIKE 'R652%')) 
    AND proc.CHARTDATE BETWEEN icu.INTIME AND icu.INTIME + INTERVAL '48' HOUR 
), 
sepsis_mortality AS ( 
    SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT icu.HADM_ID) AS sepsis_deaths 
    FROM sepsis_patients sp 
    JOIN ICUSTAYS icu ON sp.HADM_ID = icu.HADM_ID 
    JOIN ADMISSIONS adm ON adm.SUBJECT_ID = icu.SUBJECT_ID AND adm.HADM_ID = icu.HADM_ID 
    WHERE adm.DEATHTIME BETWEEN icu.INTIME AND icu.OUTTIME 
), 
non_sepsis_mortality AS ( 
    SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT icu.HADM_ID) AS non_sepsis_deaths 
    FROM ICUSTAYS icu 
    JOIN ADMISSIONS adm ON icu.HADM_ID = adm.HADM_ID 
    WHERE icu.HADM_ID NOT IN (SELECT HADM_ID FROM sepsis_patients) 
    AND adm.DEATHTIME BETWEEN icu.INTIME AND icu.OUTTIME 
), 
total_sepsis AS ( 
    SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT HADM_ID) AS total_sepsis 
    FROM sepsis_patients 
), 
total_non_sepsis AS ( 
    SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT icu.HADM_ID) AS total_non_sepsis 
    FROM ICUSTAYS icu 
    WHERE icu.HADM_ID NOT IN (SELECT HADM_ID FROM sepsis_patients) 
) 
SELECT 
    CASE WHEN ts.total_sepsis > 0 THEN sm.sepsis_deaths / ts.total_sepsis ELSE 0 END AS sepsis_mortality_rate, 
    CASE WHEN tns.total_non_sepsis > 0 THEN nsm.non_sepsis_deaths / tns.total_non_sepsis ELSE 0 END AS non_sepsis_mortality_rate 
FROM sepsis_mortality sm 
JOIN non_sepsis_mortality nsm ON 1=1 
JOIN total_sepsis ts ON 1=1 
JOIN total_non_sepsis tns ON 1=1

rules.fixed_sql:
WITH readmission AS (
    SELECT HADM_ID, COUNT(*) / COUNT(DISTINCT HADM_ID) AS readmission_rate
    FROM ADMISSIONS
    WHERE HADM_ID IN (
        SELECT HADM_ID
        FROM ADMISSIONS a1
        WHERE a1.ADMITTIME > (
            SELECT MAX(a2.DISCHTIME)
            FROM ADMISSIONS a2
            WHERE a2.HADM_ID = a1.HADM_ID
        )
    )
    GROUP BY HADM_ID
), mortality AS (
    SELECT ADMISSIONS.HADM_ID, AVG(CASE WHEN ADMISSIONS.DEATHTIME IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS mortality_rate
    FROM ADMISSIONS
    LEFT JOIN ICUSTAYS ON ADMISSIONS.HADM_ID = ICUSTAYS.HADM_ID
    WHERE ADMISSIONS.DEATHTIME BETWEEN ICUSTAYS.INTIME AND ICUSTAYS.OUTTIME
    GROUP BY ADMISSIONS.HADM_ID
)
SELECT r.readmission_rate, m.mortality_rate, COUNT(*) AS count
FROM readmission r
JOIN mortality m ON r.HADM_ID = m.HADM_ID
GROUP BY r.readmission_rate, m.mortality_rate

rules.fixed_sql:
WITH sepsis_cohort AS (
    SELECT icu_stays.hadm_id, 
           CASE WHEN EXISTS (
               SELECT 1 FROM DIAGNOSES_ICD 
               WHERE DIAGNOSES_ICD.hadm_id = icu_stays.hadm_id 
                 AND DIAGNOSES_ICD.ICD_CODE LIKE 'A41%' 
                 AND DIAGNOSES_ICD.ICD_VERSION = 10
                 AND DIAGNOSES_ICD.SEQ_NUM <= 48
           ) THEN 'Sepsis' ELSE 'No Sepsis' END AS sepsis_status
    FROM ICUSTAYS icu_stays
    JOIN PROCEDURES_ICD proc_icd ON icu_stays.hadm_id = proc_icd.hadm_id
    WHERE proc_icd.ICD_CODE LIKE '38.93%' AND proc_icd.ICD_VERSION = 9
      AND proc_icd.CHARTDATE BETWEEN icu_stays.INTIME AND icu_stays.INTIME + INTERVAL '48' HOUR
), icu_deaths AS (
    SELECT icu_stays.hadm_id
    FROM ICUSTAYS icu_stays
    JOIN ADMISSIONS adm ON icu_stays.hadm_id = adm.hadm_id
    WHERE adm.DEATHTIME BETWEEN icu_stays.INTIME AND icu_stays.OUTTIME
)
SELECT sepsis_status, COUNT(DISTINCT icu_deaths.hadm_id) / COUNT(DISTINCT sepsis_cohort.hadm_id) AS icu_mortality_rate
FROM sepsis_cohort
LEFT JOIN icu_deaths ON sepsis_cohort.hadm_id = icu_deaths.hadm_id
GROUP BY sepsis_status
